<item>
            <title>[LU-9624] enable sanity.sh test_160a failures for DNE</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9624</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I just noticed that sanity.sh test_160a is using a special &quot;err17935&quot; handler for test failures, essentially skipping the test result if run with DNE.  I suspect this is no longer needed (it dates from ancient 1.x days), and should be removed and treated like a regular error.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
